=head1 DESCRIPTION

The metadata for your tax document.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> TaxDocumentAccessToken => Str

The tax document access token, which contains information that the Tax
Settings API uses to locate the tax document.

If you update your tax registration, the existing
C<taxDocumentAccessToken> won't be valid. To get the latest token, call
the C<GetTaxRegistration> or C<ListTaxRegistrations> API operation.
This token is valid for 24 hours.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> TaxDocumentName => Str

The name of your tax document.



